529
00:40:29,667 --> 00:40:32,000
What are you talking about all of sudden?

530
00:40:32,933 --> 00:40:35,167
My CEO.

531
00:40:35,167 --> 00:40:37,700
Huh? Unbelievable.

532
00:40:37,733 --> 00:40:39,533
You.

