553
00:41:55,933 --> 00:41:57,600
Don't take his side.

554
00:41:57,600 --> 00:42:00,400
Both Mr. Chun Pil and your mom…

555
00:42:00,400 --> 00:42:02,267
My mom?

556
00:42:08,767 --> 00:42:11,667
At the moment my brother died,

557
00:42:13,100 --> 00:42:16,567
Chun Pil and Su Ji were together.

558
00:42:21,767 --> 00:42:23,133
 Mom. 

559
00:42:23,133 --> 00:42:25,033
 Mom! Mom, what's happening? 

560
00:42:25,033 --> 00:42:28,333
 Kang Hee, please call Dad for me. 

561
00:42:28,333 --> 00:42:30,533
 Please call Dad. 

562
