00:45:08,567 --> 00:45:10,333
 Then I'll wait downstairs. 

604
00:45:29,333 --> 00:45:31,100
 You heard it, right? 

605
00:45:35,667 --> 00:45:37,567
I'll get going.

606
00:48:03,700 --> 00:48:05,900
