00:51:46,967 --> 00:51:49,733
Please take this to Kang Hee's room…

636
00:51:49,733 --> 00:51:51,133
Yes.

637
00:52:15,633 --> 00:52:18,567
It's a call from Kang Hee.

638
00:52:22,133 --> 00:52:25,467
Kang Hee, how's Seoul?

639
00:52:25,467 --> 00:52:27,910
You're bored without me, aren't you?

640
00:52:28,467 --> 00:52:32,533
Bored? I have a lot to do as well.

641
00:52:32,533 --> 00:52:37,000
Like doing laundry and making calls.

642
00:52:37,000 --> 00:52:38,667
What about you?

643
00:52:38,667 --> 00:52:42,800
How are you doing? Are Yeon Soo and the others all doing well?

644
00:52:46,333 --> 00:52:49,000
Ah, you miss me that much?

645
00:52:51,733 --> 00:52:53,367
I'm in a good mood, so I'll hang up now.

646
00:52:53,367 --> 00:52:55,233
 I'm also doing well… 

647
00:52:56,967 --> 00:52:58,533
Hello?

648
00:53:03,167 --> 00:53:06,100
Take a good rest in Seoul before you come back.

649
00:53:06,100 --> 00:53:07,733
Yes.

650
00:53:10,667 --> 00:53:12,533
Why?

651
00:53:12,533 --> 00:53:13,833
Can't I just call without a reason?

652
00:53:13,833 --> 00:53:16,533
Am I your lover or something? Hang up.

653
00:53:17,400 --> 00:53:19,700
I'm swamped with work.

654
00:53:19,700 --> 00:53:21,833
Oh, yeah, yeah.

655
00:53:22,967 --> 00:53:24,800
- Yeah. 
 - I'll hang up first then.

656
00:53:24,800 --> 00:53:27,333
I'll hang up now, bye.

657
00:53:29,767 --> 00:53:31,267
Ah, okay.

658
00:53:31,267 --> 00:53:35,200
Oh, I'm doing well. We should meet sometime, it's a pity.

659
00:53:35,200 --> 00:53:36,267
Because I'm busy.

660
00:53:36,267 --> 00:53:38,190
Sure, come visit sometime.

661
00:53:38,190 --> 00:53:39,530
Yeah, okay.

662
00:53:39,533 --> 00:53:41,933
Yeah, sorry.

663
00:53:42,733 --> 00:53:44,833
Ah, I got a call from Kang Hee.

664
00:53:44,833 --> 00:53:46,933
I told her to take a good rest while she's in Seoul and then come back.

665
00:53:46,933 --> 00:53:49,000
Oh, yeah. I see.

