00:55:09,000 --> 00:55:11,367
- Thank you for your hard work. 
 - Yes.

685
00:55:14,233 --> 00:55:15,800
Kang Hee.

686
00:55:16,767 --> 00:55:18,167
Ms. Ji Kang Hee.

687
00:55:18,167 --> 00:55:19,233
Yes, Ms. Hwang.

